text: Git hit is god þæt þu wite hrædlice hwilcconcurrentesyrne on geare.
Loca hwilce dæg cumanona kalendas aprilis.
Gif he cymð on sunnandæg, þonne yrnð se concurrentunum.
Gif he cymð on monandæg, þonne yrnð se concurrentduo.
Cume swilce dæg swilce he cume, swa þu miht witan hwilc concurrent yrnð on geare.
